channel.title: PX Nibiru | New Age RSPS | Far more advanced than anything!
channel.description:
I created this project 2 months ago. I've been doing it solo this whole time. I'm looking for two people to partner up with me, as it's better to have more than one set of eyes. I have alot of plans, and I've already put some into action, already making it far different than most. There's going to be tons of features, you may as well call this RS4. My main goal is to provide 110% player & employee satisfaction. If I'm lucky, I also want to change RSPS history, and introduce a ton of new amazing flawless features to everyone. So then maybe I'll also inspire them to put their brain to actual use. That's all the info I'm releasing for now, if you're interested and want to know more. Contact me at tim.c023 via skype.
[u][b]Partner Requirements:[/b] [/u]
[ul][li]Must have well understanding of Java (and or) / HTML, PHP, HTML5, MySQL / or GFX[/li] [li]I don't ask that you're on every day, but I do ask that you're on a regular basis.[/li] [li]You must interact with the community, if not there's no point being apart in this project.[/li] [li]You must be dedicated, and prepared for a long term position..[/li][/ul]
[b] [center]That's it thanks, kind reguards[/center] [center][img]http://i45.tinypic.com/zit94w.png[/img] [Owner] Tim[/center]
